# AI Food Assistant - Project Instructions

## Project Overview
Building an AI-powered food assistant with a ChatGPT-style interface that helps users discover food, analyze ingredients, and simulate ordering from restaurants and grocery stores.

## Core Functionality
- **ChatGPT-Style Interface**: Central chat interface for natural conversation about food preferences
- **Conversational Food Discovery**: AI determines what user wants to eat through natural dialogue
- **Ingredient Analysis**: AI identifies required ingredients and suggests what user might need
- **Inventory Management**: AI helps track what ingredients user has vs. needs
- **Restaurant & Grocery Sidebar**: Side panel showing available restaurants and grocery stores
- **Order Simulation**: Simulates ordering from both restaurants and grocery stores
- **Web Scraping**: Collects restaurant menus and grocery store ingredient data

## Target Integration
- **Primary**: DoorDash and Uber Eats partnerships
- **Goal**: Pitch as integrated food assistant feature for these platforms
- **Value Prop**: Increase platform engagement by connecting cooking inspiration to ingredient delivery

## Technical Requirements

### AI/ML Components
- **Conversational AI**: Natural language processing for user interaction
- **Recipe Recommendation**: ML-powered recipe suggestions based on user preferences
- **Ingredient Recognition**: Computer vision for pantry scanning (future)
- **Voice Processing**: Speech-to-text and text-to-speech capabilities

### Integration Requirements
- **DoorDash API**: Integration for grocery/ingredient ordering
- **Uber Eats API**: Alternative ordering platform integration
- **Payment Processing**: Secure transaction handling
- **Location Services**: Delivery address management

### Data Sources
- **Recipe Databases**: Web scraping from cooking websites
- **Nutritional Data**: Ingredient nutritional information
- **Pricing Data**: Real-time ingredient pricing from delivery platforms
- **User Preferences**: Dietary restrictions, allergies, preferences storage

### Infrastructure
- **Model Hosting**: Brev.nvidia GPU deployment for AI model inference
- **Backend Services**: API layer for all integrations
- **Database**: User profiles, recipes, ingredients, order history
- **Web Scraping**: Automated recipe and ingredient data collection
- **Real-time Communication**: WebSocket for chat functionality

## User Journey
1. User opens AI Food Assistant with ChatGPT-style interface
2. User types natural language about what they want to eat
3. AI engages in conversation to understand preferences and dietary needs
4. AI suggests food options (restaurant meals OR home cooking recipes)
5. If home cooking: AI analyzes required ingredients and asks what user has
6. AI identifies missing ingredients and suggests grocery stores from sidebar
7. If restaurant meal: AI suggests restaurants from sidebar
8. User can chat to refine choices and get recommendations
9. User selects from sidebar and places simulated order
10. AI provides cooking guidance or order tracking

